ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T16:36:39.000Z","msg":"香港普遍流行德國同美洲甲由<br />\n而你相入面呢隻呢<br />\n就兩種都唔係<br />\n每一種都有唔同習性<br />\n我講個兩種得一隻走得快（仲要係好撚快）<br />\n你可以懷疑下鄰居係咪養寵物甲由走甩左<br />\n係既話你仆街得，買定滅蟲炸彈（水煙式）希望殺得"},{"pid":"ca6a93e1613f1dfd51c4e739598f29a598681973","tid":1041211,"uid":90520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3e96a74c2b932554e19c174fffb1c6882685bf0a","tid":1041211,"uid":85427,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T16:28:21.000Z","msg":"咩bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />算係中型 呢隻種嘅bb得隻蟻咁細<br />\n究極體最多一折手指咁長"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T16:41:46.000Z","msg":"係 我屋企都有<br />\n感覺上 其實唔太污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n似普通昆蟲多過係曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留明學嘢"},{"pid":"43fec3977f68b029fec93aaf1d05be84ff4af9d2","tid":1041211,"uid":238536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"790b6febe3698377b6894cc1a32c9193f4ef8f56","tid":1041211,"uid":91829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e4dd59cff0afe0752e927fe509dc6311adfe969b","tid":1041211,"uid":153722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4b82861f00b5fd3c718e26cd453b8f633908254","tid":1041211,"uid":91829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T16:12:07.000Z","msg":"呢排成日係間房到發現啲甲由仔<br />\n一發現諗住打死佢個陣 佢走得勁撚快<br />\n快到拍都拍唔撚切<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個身仲要透透地明咁 唔似以前啲甲由仔咁<br />\n好似愈嚟愈多<br />\n有無巴絲屋企啲甲由都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/01/001013_1855ec8889c778c38b8f3745b5950e51.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F01%2F001013_1855ec8889c778c38b8f3745b5950e51.png&h=09d599a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T16:12:55.000Z","msg":"用炸彈啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T16:17:02.000Z","msg":"有無邊隻炸彈用過效果幾好？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想炸撚死佢全家！<br />\n前幾日已經拍死左幾隻 全部都係呢啲啡色種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T16:46:24.000Z","msg":"用過雷達都好似ok"},{"pid":"190b5195937d01b1c40cd38d9b9cb9304ac063d4","tid":1041211,"uid":91829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T16:53:04.000Z","msg":"啱啱又拍死咗一隻<br />\n一粒米咁細 一樣係啡色<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n發現新技能 識得扮死<br />\n頭先拍咗一下好大力<br />\n見佢唔郁就用紙巾包一包住佢先<br />\n開頭以為佢死咗 點知過咗半分鐘<br />\n佢係張紙巾入面爬返出嚟 乜撚嘢事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6456b691a3fe09f071b9fcb49eceec7545bb59c4","tid":1041211,"uid":213894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T16:56:20.000Z","msg":"之前一開廚房廁所 起碼6-7隻係度<br />\n（因為家母興隔夜第日先洗碗）<br />\n<br />\n之後我真係頂唔順 買左兩舊水黑色盒仔嗰啲曱甴糖漿盒（好似叫威滅）兩舊水係真係買到超級多盒<br />\n<br />\n之後每60-70cm擺一個 重災區幾個幾個咁擺<br />\n<br />\n當然 你要做其他功夫 例如搵下佢嘅穴 清下啲唔食唔用又擺喺度嘅食物/材料"},{"pid":"9e11039e87e1373e4006161d0c016ee6d334d34f","tid":1041211,"uid":190066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T16:58:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d5f6b6f98667cf605407545a35dc4618ea22bb43","tid":1041211,"uid":153722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T16:59:54.000Z","msg":"我試過滅蟲滅蟻<br />\n但雷達殺他死個d大路野冇咩用 可能d蟲慣晒<br />\n比藥房水過買德國貴野無撚用<br />\n最後要係藥房買d中文字 cheap雞野先治到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53511af2595975d97bdaf7c71b10e85437a33f90","tid":1041211,"uid":153722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T17:02:29.000Z","msg":"小強的話<br />\n以前試過用d小強屋都work<br />\n廚廁各一<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但你個情況咁嚴重 唔係咁易殺全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eceb80772b786d948a0244bc94e0a91f943c92e8","tid":1041211,"uid":91829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6456b691a3fe09f071b9fcb49eceec7545bb59c4","tid":1041211,"uid":213894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T16:56:20.000Z","msg":"之前一開廚房廁所 起碼6-7隻係度<br />\n（因為家母興隔夜第日先洗碗）<br />\n<br />\n之後我真係頂唔順 買左兩舊水黑色盒仔嗰啲曱甴糖漿盒（好似叫威滅）兩舊水係真係買到超級多盒<br />\n<br />\n之後每60-70cm擺一個 重災區幾個幾個咁擺<br />\n<br />\n當然 你要做其他功夫 例如搵下佢嘅穴 清下啲唔食唔用又擺喺度嘅食物/材料"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T17:20:25.000Z","msg":"我會試齊曬咁多樣嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n炸彈 甲由屋"},{"pid":"7f5ec65c863fd30fdcf86605ed69a3659012d358","tid":1041211,"uid":91829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53511af2595975d97bdaf7c71b10e85437a33f90","tid":1041211,"uid":153722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T17:02:29.000Z","msg":"小強的話<br />\n以前試過用d小強屋都work<br />\n廚廁各一<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但你個情況咁嚴重 唔係咁易殺全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T17:22:27.000Z","msg":"一諗起佢全家出曬嚟攤屍就覺得嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想像唔到會有幾多隻"},{"pid":"11a37fe3942364d7dd82ff0012bb60034032c3b5","tid":1041211,"uid":38968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T17:24:52.000Z","msg":"你呢啲好似係德國強嘅Bb嚟<br />\n用大陸嘅滅蟑清試下<br />\n大陸嘢最毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4969b6ab5088f1ec2bde4e3ce4a9eb1d98654c","tid":1041211,"uid":171715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T15:54:05.000Z","msg":"我屋企有係呢隻，早排係張枱啲窿搵到佢個巢，一夜殺左廿幾隻大大小小嘅，清左三四粒蛋，用填縫膠封窿，點知呢幾日又開始見到幾隻<br />\n唉，住左十年明明一直無事，一惹到番黎真係長期搏鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家加油"}]}